a prima facie showing

28:04.552 --> 28:06.075
of irreparable harm

28:06.119 --> 28:07.207
to these children.Your Honor...

28:07.250 --> 28:08.599
I also believe that

28:08.643 --> 28:11.515
petitioner's likelihood
of success on the merits

28:11.559 --> 28:13.648
is great.Judge, the APA's amicus brief...

28:13.692 --> 28:15.171
I've read it,

28:15.215 --> 28:18.914
Ms. Cutler, and unless you
have anything new, I'm inclined

28:18.958 --> 28:20.742
to rule against
the State of Arizona

28:20.786 --> 28:22.701
and grant a preliminary...

